{"article_id":"gkYAd8lYC7j0RDcn","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"With a crucial Democratic presidential showdown in New York just a week away ,","depth":7},{"id":1,"text":"Sen. Bernard Sanders on Sunday launched a blistering assault on rival Hillary Clinton ,","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"openly questioning the former secretary of state ' s judgment","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"and saying","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"he has doubts about the type of president","depth":9},{"id":5,"text":"she would make .","depth":9},{"id":6,"text":"Mr. Sanders made the comments","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"as the Democratic presidential primary enters the home stretch .","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"The senator from Vermont","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"- fresh off a win in the Wyoming caucuses Saturday , his eighth victory in the past nine contests -","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"clearly believes","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"the momentum is on his side .","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"His campaign ,","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"which had focused almost entirely on issues such as income inequality ,","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"has entered a new phase ,","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"and Mr. Sanders ' strategy now is to discredit Mrs. Clinton among primary voters .","depth":6},{"id":16,"text":"\" I have my doubts about what kind of president she would make , \"","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"Mr. Sanders told CNN ' s \" State of the Union , \" one of four appearances","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"he made on the Sunday talk show circuit .","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"\" In terms of experience , no question","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"she has the experience . \"","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"He took his critique even further on NBC ' s \" Meet the Press , \"","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"detailing the reasons","depth":10},{"id":23,"text":"he believes","depth":10},{"id":24,"text":"Mrs. Clinton should not be president .","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"\" In terms of her judgment , something is clearly lacking , \"","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"he said .","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"\" When you vote for virtually every trade agreement","depth":11},{"id":28,"text":"that has cost workers of this country millions of jobs ,","depth":11},{"id":29,"text":"when you support and continue to support fracking","depth":12},{"id":30,"text":"despite the crisis","depth":14},{"id":31,"text":"we have","depth":14},{"id":32,"text":"in terms of clean water ,","depth":13},{"id":33,"text":"and essentially when you have a super PAC","depth":12},{"id":34,"text":"that is raising tens of millions of dollars from every special interest out there . ...","depth":12},{"id":35,"text":"The American people do not believe","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"that is the kind of president","depth":11},{"id":37,"text":"we need","depth":12},{"id":38,"text":"to make the changes in America","depth":13},{"id":39,"text":"to protect working families of this country . \"","depth":13},{"id":40,"text":"Mr. Sanders also has routinely questioned Mrs. Clinton ' s judgment","depth":5},{"id":41,"text":"because of her 2002 vote","depth":6},{"id":42,"text":"to authorize the Iraq War .","depth":6},{"id":43,"text":"Mr. Sanders defeated Mrs. Clinton in the Wyoming caucuses Saturday ,","depth":7},{"id":44,"text":"garnering 55 percent of the vote to her 44 percent .","depth":7},{"id":45,"text":"But","depth":7},{"id":46,"text":"because of the Democratic Party ' s proportional delegate allocation ,","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"each emerged from Wyoming with seven delegates .","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"Mrs. Clinton leads the delegate race 1,756 to 1,068 ,","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"according to a tally by The Associated Press .","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"Among pledged delegates , she leads 1,287 to 1,037 ,","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"and among superdelegates 469 to 31 .","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"It takes 2,383 delegates","depth":7},{"id":53,"text":"to win the Democratic presidential nomination .","depth":7},{"id":54,"text":"The Sanders campaign argues","depth":5},{"id":55,"text":"that superdelegates","depth":8},{"id":56,"text":"- party leaders and elected officials","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"free to support either candidate -","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"ultimately will switch to his side","depth":7},{"id":59,"text":"after realizing","depth":7},{"id":60,"text":"that he , not Mrs. Clinton , is the party ' s best hope","depth":8},{"id":61,"text":"to defeat a Republican such as Donald Trump or Sen. Ted Cruz in November .","depth":8},{"id":62,"text":"Mrs. Clinton has brushed off the attacks from Mr. Sanders .","depth":4},{"id":63,"text":"She told CNN on Sunday","depth":6},{"id":64,"text":"that she will have the number of delegates","depth":8},{"id":65,"text":"needed","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"to win the nomination","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"by the time","depth":8},{"id":68,"text":"the Democratic National Convention opens in July .","depth":8},{"id":69,"text":"She also is disputing the narrative","depth":8},{"id":70,"text":"that the momentum is clearly on Mr. Sanders ' side .","depth":8},{"id":71,"text":"\" Right now , I am leading him with about 2.5 million [ more ]","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"votes in the popular vote ,","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"I ' m leading in pledged delegates with a larger margin","depth":10},{"id":74,"text":"than Sen. Obama ever had over me","depth":11},{"id":75,"text":"[ in 2008 ] , \"","depth":11},{"id":76,"text":"she said .","depth":9},{"id":77,"text":"\" I feel good about the upcoming contests ,","depth":8},{"id":78,"text":"and I expect to be the nominee","depth":8},{"id":79,"text":"and will hope to have a unified Democratic Party","depth":8},{"id":80,"text":"so we can turn our attention to the Republican nominee . \"","depth":8},{"id":81,"text":"The New York primary April 19 could be a turning point in the race .","depth":3},{"id":82,"text":"The Empire State has 291 delegates at stake , by far the greatest number until the June 7 primary in California ,","depth":5},{"id":83,"text":"where 548 delegates are on the line .","depth":5},{"id":84,"text":"The latest Real Clear Politics average of all New York polls shows Mrs. Clinton with a 14-point lead over Mr. Sanders in the state .","depth":5},{"id":85,"text":"That lead , however , is shrinking .","depth":6},{"id":86,"text":"Less than two months ago , surveys showed Mrs. Clinton with an advantage of more than 20 points .","depth":6},{"id":87,"text":"Meanwhile , Mr. Sanders also has taken aim at Mrs. Clinton ' s husband , former President Bill Clinton ,","depth":5},{"id":88,"text":"for defending his 1994 anti-crime bill .","depth":5},{"id":89,"text":"Virtually everyone agrees","depth":7},{"id":90,"text":"the legislation has led to a disproportionate number of Americans","depth":9},{"id":91,"text":"- many of them black -","depth":9},{"id":92,"text":"in prison for low-level drug offenses .","depth":8},{"id":93,"text":"Mr. Clinton defended the law at a campaign event Thursday ,","depth":7},{"id":94,"text":"saying","depth":8},{"id":95,"text":"it was designed","depth":9},{"id":96,"text":"to reduce violence .","depth":9},{"id":97,"text":"Mr. Sanders","depth":7},{"id":98,"text":"- who voted for the legislation -","depth":7},{"id":99,"text":"has called on the president to apologize .","depth":6},{"id":100,"text":"But the Clinton campaign argues","depth":5},{"id":101,"text":"that the senator is twisting the facts for the sake of a convenient political attack .","depth":5},{"id":102,"text":"\" I think","depth":7},{"id":103,"text":"he ' s airbrushing history , \"","depth":7},{"id":104,"text":"Clinton campaign chairman John Podesta told ABC ' s \" This Week.","depth":6},{"id":105,"text":"\" \" He won ' t do what the president has done ,","depth":9},{"id":106,"text":"what Hillary has reiterated ,","depth":9},{"id":107,"text":"which is to say","depth":9},{"id":108,"text":"this thing has made the problems worse in some ways .","depth":9},{"id":109,"text":"We need to fix it .","depth":7},{"id":110,"text":"And that ' s why","depth":8},{"id":111,"text":"[ Mrs. Clinton ]","depth":9},{"id":112,"text":"has put on a comprehensive reform","depth":9},{"id":113,"text":"to end the era of mass incarceration","depth":8},{"id":114,"text":"and to really get the job done","depth":9},{"id":115,"text":"when it comes to dealing with the problem of overincarceration ,","depth":10},{"id":116,"text":"what that ' s done to communities all across the country . \"","depth":10}],"relations":[{"parent":233,"left":197,"right":232,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":197,"left":159,"right":196,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":159,"left":128,"right":158,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":128,"left":124,"right":127,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":124,"left":122,"right":123,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":122,"left":118,"right":121,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":118,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":121,"left":2,"right":120,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":120,"left":3,"right":119,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":119,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":123,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":127,"left":125,"right":126,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":125,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":126,"left":10,"right":11,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":158,"left":155,"right":157,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":155,"left":131,"right":154,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":131,"left":130,"right":15,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":130,"left":129,"right":14,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":129,"left":12,"right":13,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":154,"left":135,"r